name: Hello, I am Ace Subido
body:
### Work and Experiments
I used to code at the front-end.

Then I worked back-ends.

For sometime I also dealt with servers, databases and creating software as services.

Had a huge chunk of time leading agile development teams.

Right now, I just design and build things from the ground up.
tagline: I love God. I enjoy designing and building software.
